1
00:01:43,665 --> 00:01:44,326
[SIGHS]

2
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,460
- I HOPE YOU UNDERSTAND
OUR POSITION, MIROKU.

3
00:01:46,493 --> 00:01:48,693
WE CAN'T TAKE THAT GIRL WITH US.

4
00:01:48,726 --> 00:01:49,760
- I KNOW.

5
00:01:49,793 --> 00:01:52,393
- STILL, WE CANNOT SIMPLY
ABANDON THE ORPHAN CHILD.

6
00:01:52,426 --> 00:01:55,893
- IT'S HER!
- WE HAVE FOUND KOHARU!

7
00:01:58,860 --> 00:02:00,693
[GASPS]

8
00:02:01,526 --> 00:02:02,493
- THE FEUDAL ERA.

9
00:02:02,526 --> 00:02:05,993
KOHARU HAD LOST HER ENTIRE
FAMILY IN THE WAR

10
00:02:06,026 --> 00:02:10,293
AND WAS FORCED BY HER FOSTER
FATHER TO WORK DAY AND NIGHT.

11
00:02:10,326 --> 00:02:12,460
THEN, ONE DAY--

12
00:02:12,493 --> 00:02:13,760
- HERE. EAT UP.

13
00:02:13,793 --> 00:02:16,026
- YOUNG MIROKU CAME
TO THE VILLAGE

14
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:20,193
TO PERFORM AN EXORCISM
AND MET KOHARU.

15
00:02:22,726 --> 00:02:28,326
- MIROKU, I CANNOT
BEAR TO BE PARTED AGAIN
AFTER SUCH A SHORT TIME.

16
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,960
- TRY TO UNDERSTAND, KOHARU.

17
00:02:31,693 --> 00:02:33,393
I CANNOT GUARANTEE
THAT I WOULD ALWAYS

18
00:02:33,426 --> 00:02:36,560
BE ABLE TO PROTECT YOU
IN TIMES OF BATTLE.

19
00:02:36,593 --> 00:02:38,460
YOU SEE, THE DEMON I PURSUE

20
00:02:38,493 --> 00:02:42,060
IS MORE DEVIOUS AND
FORMIDABLE THAN ANY OTHER.

21
00:02:42,093 --> 00:02:44,060
[BIRD SHRIEKS]

22
00:02:44,093 --> 00:02:45,760
KOHARU...LISTEN.

23
00:02:45,793 --> 00:02:50,160
YOU ARE ABOUT TO COMMENCE
A NEW LIFE IN A NEW VILLAGE.

24
00:02:50,193 --> 00:02:52,560
I KNOW YOU MUST BE AFRAID.

25
00:02:52,593 --> 00:02:57,793
LIFE ITSELF IS A FRIGHTENING
IMAGE FOR EVERY HUMAN BEING.

26
00:02:57,826 --> 00:02:59,226
- HUH?

27
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,826
- IN MY RIGHT HAND IS A HOLE,

28
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:04,360
CAPABLE OF DRAWING EVERYTHING
IN ITS PATH INTO THE VOID.

29
00:03:04,393 --> 00:03:06,893
A WIND TUNNEL, IF YOU WILL.

30
00:03:06,926 --> 00:03:10,960
A CURSE WAS PLACED
UPON MY FAMILY IN
MY GRANDFATHER'S TIME.

31
00:03:10,993 --> 00:03:13,626
HE AND MY FATHER WERE
EVENTUALLY SUCKED UP

32
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:16,060
INTO THE WIND TUNNELS
IN THEIR OWN HANDS.

33
00:03:16,093 --> 00:03:19,593
IN TIME, EVENTUALLY I, TOO,
WILL BE DRAWN INTO

34
00:03:19,626 --> 00:03:22,360
THE TERRIBLE NOTHINGNESS
OF MY OWN HAND.

35
00:03:22,393 --> 00:03:24,926
DESPITE THAT, I MADE UP
MY MIND TO USE

36
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:27,093
THIS TERRIBLE CURSE
AS MY STRENGTH.

37
00:03:27,126 --> 00:03:31,226
THE WIND TUNNEL ALLOWS
A MERE HUMAN LIKE MYSELF

38
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:33,060
TO TAKE ON DEMONS.

39
00:03:33,093 --> 00:03:36,926
SO I'VE COME TO THINK MY CURSE
IS ALSO MY GREATEST STRENGTH

40
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:39,160
TO BATTLE AGAINST EVIL.

41
00:03:39,193 --> 00:03:41,193
[SIGHS]

42
00:03:41,226 --> 00:03:44,726
- MIROKU IS TREMBLING.

43
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:50,393
IS MIROKU'S TALE NOTHING
MORE THAN A DECEPTION?

44
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:54,226
BEING STRONG IN LIFE...

45
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,626
IT'S NOT EASY.

46
00:03:55,660 --> 00:04:00,760
OVERCOMING UNCERTAINTIES
IS DIFFICULT.

47
00:04:10,893 --> 00:04:12,826
- HUH?

48
00:04:18,793 --> 00:04:21,526
- WE WERE SEARCHING FOR
A NEW PLACE FOR KOHARU TO LIVE

49
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:27,060
WHEN WE WERE ATTACKED
BY SOME VILLAGERS WHOSE
SOULS HAD BEEN STOLEN.

50
00:04:27,093 --> 00:04:29,160
[SHOUTING]

51
00:04:30,393 --> 00:04:32,660
- I DON'T THINK SO!

52
00:04:35,093 --> 00:04:40,093
- INUYASHA WAS FORCED TO FIGHT
THEM WITHOUT HARMING THEM.

53
00:04:40,126 --> 00:04:43,126
- SANGO WAS HIT
BY HER OWN WEAPON.

54
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,126
- AAH!

55
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,160
- WHOA! WHOA!

56
00:04:45,193 --> 00:04:48,860
- AND A GHOSTLY WHITE DEMON
STOLE KOHARU'S SOUL,

57
00:04:48,893 --> 00:04:51,560
AS WELL AS MY OWN!

58
00:04:51,593 --> 00:04:53,326
BE CAREFUL, EVERYONE.

59
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,660
BEWARE OF THE MIRROR!

60
00:05:11,126 --> 00:05:12,526
[GASPS]

61
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,526
- OH!

62
00:05:15,993 --> 00:05:17,426
- HOW STRANGE.

63
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:20,226
I CANNOT SUBDUE HER SOUL.

64
00:05:22,026 --> 00:05:26,360
STILL, YOU ARE UNABLE
TO MOVE, ARE YOU NOT?

65
00:05:26,393 --> 00:05:31,393
I DESIRE THE SHARD OF THE SACRED
JEWEL THAT YOU POSSESS.

66
00:05:31,426 --> 00:05:33,260
GIVE IT TO ME.

67
00:05:33,293 --> 00:05:35,393
[GASPS]

68
00:05:41,293 --> 00:05:43,526
- MIROKU.

69
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,126
[GRUNTING]

70
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,993
- KOHARU!

71
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:52,326
- UGH!

72
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,426
AAH!

73
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:54,360
[SIGHS]

74
00:05:54,393 --> 00:05:55,893
- WHAT ON EARTH IS GOING ON?

75
00:05:55,926 --> 00:05:59,693
- KAGOME! SHIPPO!
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

76
00:06:03,493 --> 00:06:07,060
- HOW IS SHE ABLE TO MOVE STILL?

77
00:06:07,093 --> 00:06:08,526
[GRUNTS]

78
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,960
- SANGO! KAGOME!

79
00:06:09,993 --> 00:06:13,360
SHE'S THE OTHER DEMON!

80
00:06:13,393 --> 00:06:15,460
[GROWLING]

81
00:06:18,226 --> 00:06:19,126
[SIGHS]

82
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:23,060
- KAGOME! ARE YOU HARMED?
WHAT HAS SHE DONE?

83
00:06:23,093 --> 00:06:24,760
[SIGHING]

84
00:06:24,793 --> 00:06:26,560
KIRARA! IT'S YOU!

85
00:06:26,593 --> 00:06:27,993
UH-OH!

86
00:06:28,026 --> 00:06:28,893
KAGOME!

87
00:06:28,926 --> 00:06:30,826
- SHIPPO, WHAT EXACTLY
WENT ON HERE?

88
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,893
- MIROKU, DIDN'T YOU SEE
THE WHITE DEMON?

89
00:06:32,926 --> 00:06:37,260
SHE WAS TRYING TO DRAW KAGOME'S
SOUL INTO HER EVIL MIRROR.

90
00:06:37,293 --> 00:06:40,026
- KAGOME'S SOUL?

91
00:06:41,926 --> 00:06:43,326
- UGH!

92
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,860
[SHOUTING]

93
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:49,760
- DEAD SOUL BLADES!

94
00:06:53,993 --> 00:06:56,126
[SHOUTING]

95
00:07:01,226 --> 00:07:02,960
- WHAT IS WRONG, INUYASHA?

96
00:07:02,993 --> 00:07:06,826
YOU DO NOTHING
BUT FLEE FROM ME.

97
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:08,360
THIS LEADS ME TO ONE BELIEF:

98
00:07:08,393 --> 00:07:10,726
YOU'VE NOT RECOVERED
FROM YOUR INJURIES.

99
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:13,026
- I ONLY NEED ONE
GOOD ATTACK ON HER.

100
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:17,026
IF I CAN GET ONE GOOD SWING IN,
MY ARM CAN HANDLE IT.

101
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:18,426
- PREPARE TO DIE...

102
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:22,260
IN THE NAME OF MY COMRADES!

103
00:07:22,293 --> 00:07:23,560
- HE'S SO FAST!

104
00:07:23,593 --> 00:07:27,660
WHEN I FOUGHT THAT FOOL
KOGA WHO HAD BEEN
DECEIVED BY NARAKU...

105
00:07:27,693 --> 00:07:29,060
- IRON REAPER!

106
00:07:29,093 --> 00:07:34,593
- MY RIGHT ARM WAS WOUNDED
BY THE POWER OF THAT
FAKE SACRED JEWEL SHARD.

107
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:37,326
MY ARM HAS NOT YET RECOVERED.

108
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:40,693
STILL, IF I CAN CUT THROUGH
THE WIND SCAR IN ONE MOVE,

109
00:07:40,726 --> 00:07:43,426
I CAN BRING HER DOWN.

110
00:08:00,993 --> 00:08:03,326
- I NEVER IMAGINED
THAT THIS YOUNG UPSTART

111
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:08,393
WOULD TRY SOMETHING
ELABORATE SUCH AS
A WIND SCAR TO BATTLE ME.

112
00:08:12,926 --> 00:08:14,560
WHEN I FIRST MET HIM IN BATTLE,

113
00:08:14,593 --> 00:08:17,693
THE SACRED ARROW DISPELLED
MY WIND ASSAULT

114
00:08:17,726 --> 00:08:20,493
AND CREATED A WIND SCAR.

115
00:08:23,526 --> 00:08:24,560
IMPOSSIBLE!

116
00:08:24,593 --> 00:08:28,893
KAGOME'S SACRED ARROW WAS
PURIFYING MY WIND POWERS!

117
00:08:28,926 --> 00:08:32,693
- JUST AS I THOUGHT.
THE WIND HAS DISAPPEARED.

118
00:08:32,726 --> 00:08:34,026
- SUCH A FOOL!

119
00:08:34,060 --> 00:08:37,226
I ONLY NEED TO CREATE MORE!

120
00:08:40,793 --> 00:08:46,593
THE WIND SCAR IS CREATED
WHEN THE DEMONIC WINDS COLLIDE.

121
00:08:48,926 --> 00:08:51,360
I CONTROL ALL WIND.

122
00:08:51,393 --> 00:08:52,260
- ARRGH!

123
00:08:52,293 --> 00:08:53,826
- IF NOT FOR THAT ARROW,

124
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:57,593
A WIND SCAR WOULD
NEVER HAVE FORMED.

125
00:09:04,793 --> 00:09:06,193
- NO GOOD.
IT WON'T WORK.

126
00:09:06,226 --> 00:09:10,593
THE WIND SCAR WON'T FORM WITHIN
THE WIND SHE'S CREATED.

127
00:09:13,226 --> 00:09:14,960
- HMM.

128
00:09:21,093 --> 00:09:21,893
- WAIT!

129
00:09:21,926 --> 00:09:23,460
THAT WAS A WIND SCAR!

130
00:09:23,493 --> 00:09:24,926
HOW CAN THAT BE?

131
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,793
WHAT DOES IT MEAN?

132
00:09:25,826 --> 00:09:29,260
IS HER CONTROL OVER
THE WIND WEAKENING?

133
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:33,260
THIS IS MY ONLY CHANCE.

134
00:09:34,193 --> 00:09:37,893
I COULD SLAY HER NOW,
WITH THE WIND SCAR.

135
00:09:37,926 --> 00:09:39,160
[PANTING]

136
00:09:39,193 --> 00:09:40,126
- MIROKU, LOOK!

137
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:42,793
INUYASHA IS WIELDING
HIS TETSUSAIGA.

138
00:09:42,826 --> 00:09:45,093
HE WILL CUT THROUGH
THE WIND SCAR.

139
00:09:45,126 --> 00:09:46,026
- I MUST STOP HIM.

140
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:48,426
HE DOES NOT YET KNOW
ABOUT THE SECOND DEMON,

141
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:49,893
THE SOUL-THIEVING APPARITION.

142
00:09:49,926 --> 00:09:52,660
SANGO'S WEAPON WAS
THRUST BACK AT HER.

143
00:09:52,693 --> 00:09:55,560
AND THE WIND SCAR WILL BE
HURLED BACK AT INUYASHA!

144
00:09:55,593 --> 00:09:59,026
- I SEE IT!
- I ALLOWED YOU TO SEE IT!

145
00:09:59,060 --> 00:09:59,926
- THE WIND SCAR!

146
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:03,426
- YOU WISH TO SLICE
THROUGH IT, I IMAGINE.

147
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:06,760
- YOU ARE MINE!

148
00:10:06,793 --> 00:10:08,826
[LAUGHTER]

149
00:10:10,926 --> 00:10:14,093
- NOW, PERISH!

150
00:10:19,426 --> 00:10:22,026
- WHAT?

151
00:10:22,060 --> 00:10:25,026
AAH!

152
00:10:28,326 --> 00:10:31,460
AAH!

153
00:10:50,226 --> 00:10:53,860
- INUYASHA!
- INUYASHA!

154
00:11:00,626 --> 00:11:02,626
[SOFT THUNDER]

155
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,760
[GRUNTING]

156
00:11:23,060 --> 00:11:25,760
- IT'S HIM!

157
00:11:25,793 --> 00:11:27,926
NARAKU!

158
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:31,126
[CACKLING]

159
00:11:31,982 --> 00:11:33,948
- THAT WAS INDEED SIMPLE ENOUGH.

160
00:11:33,982 --> 00:11:36,382
I CAME SO THAT I COULD
ASK YOU IN PERSON

161
00:11:36,415 --> 00:11:39,848
HOW IT FELT TO HAVE YOUR OWN
POWER TURNED AGAINST YOU,

162
00:11:39,882 --> 00:11:42,948
AND VERY EASILY,
I MIGHT ADD.

163
00:11:43,315 --> 00:11:46,915
- I AM INDEED HONORED
FOR YOUR PRESENCE, NARAKU.

164
00:11:46,948 --> 00:11:49,315
I RATHER EXPECTED
A DEMON PUPPET.

165
00:11:49,348 --> 00:11:52,615
YOU ARE A COWARD WHO NEVER
SULLIES HIS OWN HANDS,

166
00:11:52,648 --> 00:11:54,548
WHO KNOWS ONLY
HOW TO LAY TRAPS.

167
00:11:54,582 --> 00:11:55,648
YOU MUST HAVE BEEN
FALSELY CONFIDENT

168
00:11:55,682 --> 00:11:59,282
OR ELSE YOU WOULD NOT HAVE
DARED SHOW YOUR FACE.

169
00:11:59,315 --> 00:12:00,348
- THE WIND TUNNEL.

170
00:12:00,382 --> 00:12:04,682
YOU ARE FREE TO DRAW
ANYTHING INTO YOUR VOID.

171
00:12:04,715 --> 00:12:08,948
BUT SURELY, EVEN YOU COULD
NOT BE THAT FOOLISH, MONK.

172
00:12:08,982 --> 00:12:14,115
- THE SOULS OF KAGOME
AND THE VILLAGERS ARE
LOCKED WITHIN THAT MIRROR.

173
00:12:16,582 --> 00:12:18,448
- MY COURSE OF ACTION
WAS SIMPLE.

174
00:12:18,482 --> 00:12:21,815
I CREATED WIND AND VOID
AS INCARNATIONS OF MYSELF,

175
00:12:21,848 --> 00:12:25,582
AND YET WITNESSED THE DAMAGE
I WAS ABLE TO INFLICT.

176
00:12:25,615 --> 00:12:26,748
- INCARNATIONS?

177
00:12:26,782 --> 00:12:28,415
SO MY SUSPICIONS WERE CORRECT.

178
00:12:28,448 --> 00:12:30,282
NARAKU'S POWER HAS
INCREASED DRASTICALLY

179
00:12:30,315 --> 00:12:32,648
IF HE IS CAPABLE OF
THIS LEVEL OF SORCERY.

180
00:12:32,682 --> 00:12:35,382
WE HAVE FOUGHT KAGURA,
THE WIND SORCERESS, ONCE BEFORE.

181
00:12:35,415 --> 00:12:37,815
AND THIS OTHER, SHE IS--
WAIT.

182
00:12:37,848 --> 00:12:40,415
THAT IS WHY WE COULD NOT
SENSE ITS EVIL.

183
00:12:40,448 --> 00:12:41,415
IT HAS NO PRESENCE.

184
00:12:41,448 --> 00:12:43,248
IT'S NO WONDER THE SITUATION
WENT UNNOTICED

185
00:12:43,282 --> 00:12:44,415
UNTIL IT WAS TOO LATE.

186
00:12:44,448 --> 00:12:46,315
- INUYASHA, CAN YOU HEAR ME?

187
00:12:46,348 --> 00:12:48,182
INUYASHA!

188
00:12:50,215 --> 00:12:52,148
[GROANS]

189
00:12:54,748 --> 00:12:56,615
- KIRARA.

190
00:12:57,382 --> 00:12:59,415
I NEED YOU TO DO SOMETHING.

191
00:12:59,448 --> 00:13:01,548
TAKE ME ON YOUR BACK.

192
00:13:01,582 --> 00:13:02,548
KIRARA.

193
00:13:02,582 --> 00:13:04,982
I NEED TO BE WITH INUYASHA.

194
00:13:05,015 --> 00:13:07,348
- HAVE WE NOT SPOKEN
LONG ENOUGH?

195
00:13:07,382 --> 00:13:12,282
SHALL WE TAKE INUYASHA'S HEAD
ALONG WITH US AS A TROPHY?

196
00:13:12,315 --> 00:13:13,582
NO?

197
00:13:13,615 --> 00:13:18,815
DID YOU NOT WANT TO TELL
THAT WOMAN THAT INUYASHA
HAD BEEN SLAIN?

198
00:13:18,848 --> 00:13:23,248
I WAS UNDER THE IMPRESSION
THAT THIS IS WHAT YOU DESIRED.

199
00:13:24,615 --> 00:13:25,515
- TRUE ENOUGH.

200
00:13:25,548 --> 00:13:27,548
IT WAS ONLY THROUGH
HER COOPERATION

201
00:13:27,582 --> 00:13:30,882
THAT I WAS ABLE
TO CREATE YOU AND KANNA.

202
00:13:30,915 --> 00:13:33,715
WHAT EMOTIONS WOULD
RISE ON HER FACE

203
00:13:33,748 --> 00:13:37,648
IF I WERE TO SHOW HER
INUYASHA'S HEAD, I WONDER?

204
00:13:37,682 --> 00:13:38,648
- HOW CAN THAT BE?

205
00:13:38,682 --> 00:13:42,582
NARAKU'S SACRED JEWEL
FRAGMENT IS NEARLY WHOLE.

206
00:13:42,615 --> 00:13:45,048
- YOU SUGGESTED EARLIER
THAT I DO EVERYTHING

207
00:13:45,082 --> 00:13:47,848
TO AVOID SULLYING MY OWN HANDS.

208
00:13:47,882 --> 00:13:51,048
EVEN THE MIGHTIEST ARE
INFERIOR TO SOMEONE.

209
00:13:51,082 --> 00:13:57,482
A WOMAN ATTEMPTED TO USE ME
SO THAT I WOULD MURDER
INUYASHA FOR HER.

210
00:13:57,515 --> 00:13:58,848
- A WOMAN?

211
00:13:58,882 --> 00:13:59,782
YOU DON'T MEAN--

212
00:13:59,815 --> 00:14:04,115
- HMM. SHE IS SOME
PIECE OF WORK, THAT KIKYO.

213
00:14:04,148 --> 00:14:07,415
- K-KIKYO.

214
00:14:07,448 --> 00:14:09,682
- INUYASHA!
YOU'RE ALIVE!

215
00:14:09,715 --> 00:14:11,215
THANK THE HEAVENS!

216
00:14:11,248 --> 00:14:17,548
- KIKYO PERSONALLY HANDED
THIS SACRED JEWEL SHARD
TO ME OF HER OWN FREE WILL.

217
00:14:17,582 --> 00:14:19,082
[GRUNTING]

218
00:14:19,115 --> 00:14:21,115
- KIKYO!

219
00:14:22,015 --> 00:14:25,548
- SHE WISHES TO GAZE
UPON YOUR FACE...

220
00:14:25,582 --> 00:14:28,915
AFTER YOU'RE GOOD AND DEAD!

221
00:14:29,982 --> 00:14:32,715
- AAH!
SHIPPO, STAY DOWN!

222
00:14:33,948 --> 00:14:35,415
AAH!

223
00:14:35,448 --> 00:14:36,548
- MIROKU!

224
00:14:36,582 --> 00:14:39,382
- NOW, GIVE ME YOUR HEAD!

225
00:14:48,815 --> 00:14:51,048
- THAT'S KAGOME'S ARROW!

226
00:14:51,082 --> 00:14:53,048
KAGOME!

227
00:14:58,148 --> 00:14:59,615
- HER AGAIN?

228
00:14:59,648 --> 00:15:01,448
YOU FAILED ME, KANNA!

229
00:15:01,482 --> 00:15:04,882
WHY DID YOU NOT STEAL HER SOUL?

230
00:15:05,648 --> 00:15:08,015
- HER SOUL IS SPILLING
OUT OF THE MIRROR.

231
00:15:08,048 --> 00:15:11,982
DOES THIS GIRL POSSESS
SUCH AN ENORMOUS SOUL?

232
00:15:18,815 --> 00:15:20,115
[MOANS]

233
00:15:20,148 --> 00:15:21,048
- KAGOME!

234
00:15:21,082 --> 00:15:23,348
- YOU DON'T NEED
TO WORRY ABOUT ME.

235
00:15:23,382 --> 00:15:25,015
HOW'S INUYASHA?

236
00:15:25,048 --> 00:15:26,148
- WELL, HE'S ALIVE,

237
00:15:26,182 --> 00:15:31,015
BUT HE'S SO BADLY WOUNDED
THAT HE'S UNABLE TO MOVE.

238
00:15:31,048 --> 00:15:32,982
[GASPS]

239
00:15:33,015 --> 00:15:34,782
- KAGOME!

240
00:15:34,815 --> 00:15:38,548
- I'M SO GLAD
YOU'RE ALIVE, INUYASHA.

241
00:15:38,582 --> 00:15:40,948
- I'M SO HAPPY.

242
00:15:42,915 --> 00:15:43,948
HOW DID THIS HAPPEN?

243
00:15:43,982 --> 00:15:48,382
HOW DID NARAKU GET AHOLD
OF THE SACRED JEWEL SHARD?

244
00:15:54,082 --> 00:15:59,715
IT IS THE VERY SAME SHARD
THAT KIKYO STOLE AWAY FROM ME.

245
00:16:03,148 --> 00:16:06,748
WAS IT HER THAT
GAVE IT TO NARAKU?

246
00:16:09,082 --> 00:16:14,348
THOSE SHARDS THAT WE WORKED
SO HARD TO COLLECT, ONE BY ONE.

247
00:16:14,382 --> 00:16:17,115
DID KIKYO GIVE THEM TO NARAKU?

248
00:16:17,148 --> 00:16:20,648
EVEN SO, AFTER SHE COMMITTED
SUCH A VILE ACT,

249
00:16:20,682 --> 00:16:22,682
INUYASHA STILL LOVES HER.

250
00:16:22,715 --> 00:16:24,815
EVEN THOUGH HE'S
THIS BADLY WOUNDED,

251
00:16:24,848 --> 00:16:27,515
HE CANNOT FORGET HER.

252
00:16:31,782 --> 00:16:35,682
- WOMAN, PASS THIS MESSAGE
ON TO INUYASHA.

253
00:16:35,715 --> 00:16:38,648
IF HE MUST HATE SOMEONE,
THEN HATE KIKYO,

254
00:16:38,682 --> 00:16:44,482
FOR THE ONLY THING
SHE DESIRES IS INUYASHA'S DEATH.

255
00:16:44,515 --> 00:16:47,048
- I'M TIRED OF HEARING
YOUR VOICE.

256
00:16:47,082 --> 00:16:48,982
YOU MAKE ME SICK!

257
00:16:49,915 --> 00:16:51,215
TAKE THIS!

258
00:16:51,248 --> 00:16:52,348
- DON'T DO IT, KAGOME!

259
00:16:52,382 --> 00:16:58,082
IT WILL FIRE BACK AT YOU EXACTLY
LIKE THE TETSUSAIGA DID.

260
00:16:58,115 --> 00:17:00,015
- I GUARANTEE IT WON'T.

261
00:17:00,048 --> 00:17:03,815
MY ARROW ONLY STRIKES EVIL.

262
00:17:07,648 --> 00:17:09,315
[GASPS]

263
00:17:31,665 --> 00:17:33,132
[GASPS]

264
00:17:33,165 --> 00:17:35,398
- THE ARROW.

265
00:17:36,865 --> 00:17:40,798
- THE ARROW IS STARTING
TO PIERCE THE MIRROR!

266
00:17:44,598 --> 00:17:46,632
- THE ARROW WENT THROUGH.

267
00:17:46,665 --> 00:17:48,665
IT DIDN'T DEFLECT.

268
00:17:48,698 --> 00:17:49,732
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

269
00:17:49,765 --> 00:17:52,132
WHY DID IT NOT
STRIKE BACK AT HER?

270
00:17:52,165 --> 00:17:53,998
- I UNDERSTAND.

271
00:17:54,032 --> 00:17:58,332
THE ARROW IS MADE UP OF SOULS.

272
00:17:58,365 --> 00:18:01,265
THE MIRROR IS ENTIRELY FILLED.

273
00:18:01,298 --> 00:18:04,265
UNLESS THE SOULS ARE RELEASED,

274
00:18:04,298 --> 00:18:07,065
THE MIRROR WILL BURST.

275
00:18:22,698 --> 00:18:24,732
[WHIMPERING]

276
00:18:38,898 --> 00:18:41,598
- THE SOULS HAVE RETURNED
TO THEIR BODIES.

277
00:18:41,632 --> 00:18:44,098
MIROKU! USE THE WIND TUNNEL!

278
00:18:44,132 --> 00:18:46,098
- RIGHT.

279
00:18:47,332 --> 00:18:48,532
- WHAT HAPPENED?

280
00:18:48,565 --> 00:18:50,832
[GASPING]
MIROKU!

281
00:18:52,232 --> 00:18:54,465
- WIND TUNNEL!

282
00:18:55,265 --> 00:19:01,198
- LIFE ITSELF IS A FRIGHTENING
IMAGE FOR EVERY HUMAN BEING.

283
00:19:01,232 --> 00:19:02,698
IN MY RIGHT HAND IS A HOLE

284
00:19:02,732 --> 00:19:05,398
CAPABLE OF DRAWING EVERYTHING
IN ITS PATH INTO THE VOID.

285
00:19:05,432 --> 00:19:11,998
IN TIME, EVENTUALLY I, TOO,
WILL BE DRAWN INTO THE TERRIBLE
NOTHINGNESS OF MY OWN HAND.

286
00:19:12,032 --> 00:19:17,765
BEING STRONG IN LIFE...
IT'S NOT EASY.

287
00:19:17,798 --> 00:19:22,398
OVERCOMING UNCERTAINTIES
IS DIFFICULT.

288
00:19:34,998 --> 00:19:37,098
- AAH!

289
00:19:38,598 --> 00:19:41,432
CURSE THEM!
THEY'VE ESCAPED!

290
00:19:41,465 --> 00:19:43,832
- WE SHALL ALLOW YOU
TO LIVE FOR A WHILE YET.

291
00:19:43,865 --> 00:19:48,432
THE SACRED JEWEL WILL
CONTINUE TO BESTOW ME
WITH MORE AND MORE POWER.

292
00:19:48,465 --> 00:19:55,398
LET US ALL RELISH
THE IMMEASURABLE POWER OF
THE SACRED JEWEL, SHALL WE?

293
00:20:05,432 --> 00:20:08,098
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

294
00:20:14,898 --> 00:20:17,632
- HOW WAS IT WE ALL
AWOKE IN THE FIELDS?

295
00:20:17,665 --> 00:20:20,832
- I'M FINDING IT HARD TO
REMEMBER ANYTHING AT ALL.

296
00:20:20,865 --> 00:20:23,465
- SAME FOR ME.

297
00:20:56,365 --> 00:20:59,065
- HEY!
CHEER UP, WOULD YOU?

298
00:20:59,098 --> 00:21:00,865
BUT I SUPPOSE
IT'S NOT THAT EASY,

299
00:21:00,898 --> 00:21:03,198
NOT AFTER EVERYTHING
THAT WE'VE BEEN THROUGH.

300
00:21:03,232 --> 00:21:09,098
NARAKU POSSESSES NEARLY ALL
OF THE SACRED JEWEL SHARDS.

301
00:21:09,965 --> 00:21:10,765
WHAT AM I THINKING?

302
00:21:10,798 --> 00:21:13,132
WE CAN'T GIVE UP
AT A TIME LIKE THIS!

303
00:21:13,165 --> 00:21:14,965
I'VE GOT THIS THING ALL WRONG!

304
00:21:14,998 --> 00:21:16,965
WE MUST POSSESS INCREDIBLE
POWERS OURSELVES

305
00:21:16,998 --> 00:21:21,698
TO BE ABLE TO SURVIVE
A CONFLICT WITH THE NEARLY
INVINCIBLE NARAKU

306
00:21:21,732 --> 00:21:24,132
AND LIVE TO TELL IT.

307
00:21:24,698 --> 00:21:27,298
HOW'S INUYASHA DOING?
ANY BETTER?

308
00:21:27,332 --> 00:21:29,432
- THE HERBAL REMEDIES
SEEM TO BE HELPING.

309
00:21:29,465 --> 00:21:31,498
HIS FEVER'S DROPPED,
AND HE'S SOUND ASLEEP.

310
00:21:31,532 --> 00:21:34,532
I'M GOING OUT TO SEARCH
FOR SOME MORE HERBS NOW.

311
00:21:34,565 --> 00:21:36,932
- KIRARA AND I WILL
COME ALONG AND HELP YOU,

312
00:21:36,965 --> 00:21:41,198
BECAUSE WE'RE THE ONLY ONES
AROUND HERE WITH ENOUGH ENERGY.

313
00:21:41,232 --> 00:21:42,098
[MEOW]

314
00:21:42,132 --> 00:21:44,532
- THANKS, YOU TWO.

315
00:21:51,665 --> 00:21:56,532
- KIKYO HANDED OVER THE SACRED
JEWEL SHARD TO NARAKU.

316
00:21:57,232 --> 00:22:00,198
KIKYO, WHO HAD DIED ONCE...

317
00:22:00,898 --> 00:22:04,565
THEN ROSE AGAIN WITH
A BODY MADE OF CLAY.

318
00:22:04,598 --> 00:22:06,565
KIKYO, WHO DESPISES ME,

319
00:22:06,598 --> 00:22:10,332
WHO TRIED TO MURDER KAGOME.

320
00:22:12,532 --> 00:22:14,098
WHERE ARE YOU...

321
00:22:14,132 --> 00:22:16,998
MY KIKYO?

322
00:22:30,617 --> 00:22:34,517
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

323
00:23:57,984 --> 00:24:02,545
- KIKYO HAS GIVEN NARAKU
THE SACRED JEWEL SHARD
SHE STOLE FROM ME.

324
00:24:02,578 --> 00:24:04,511
NARAKU'S POWER
CONTINUES TO INCREASE,

325
00:24:04,545 --> 00:24:08,345
AND HE SENDS INCARNATIONS OF
HIMSELF TO HUNT DOWN INUYASHA.

326
00:24:08,378 --> 00:24:12,611
THE MIND-READING GOSHINKI SINKS
HIS FANGS INTO TETSUSAIGA.

327
00:24:12,645 --> 00:24:16,178
OH, NO!
INUYASHA DOESN'T STAND A CHANCE!

328
00:24:16,211 --> 00:24:19,811
WAIT!
WHAT'S HAPPENED TO YOU?

329
00:24:19,845 --> 00:24:21,645
NEXT TIME...

330
00:24:22,445 --> 00:24:23,445
SEE YOU SOON.

